<ul><li><strong>Related Resources</strong><ul><li>Hack Biodesign: An Integrative STEAM Education Platform for Biology, Engineering, and Design <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8615404">https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/8615404</a></li><li>Humans are still evolving—and we can watch it happen <a href="https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/05/humans-are-still-evolving-and-we-can-watch-it-happen">https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2016/05/humans-are-still-evolving-and-we-can-watch-it-happen</a></li><li>Biomimicry Institue <a href="https://biomimicry.org/">https://biomimicry.org/</a></li><li>Production of healthy cloned mice from bodies frozen at −20°C for 16 years <a href="https://www.pnas.org/content/105/45/17318">https://www.pnas.org/content/105/45/17318</a></li><li>Sequence-programmable covalent bonding of designed DNA assemblies <a href="https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/4/8/eaau1157">https://advances.sciencemag.org/content/4/8/eaau1157</a></li><li>Fold it <a href="https://fold.it/portal/">https://fold.it/portal/</a></li><li>Customizing cell signaling using engineered genetic logic circuits <a href="https://www.cell.com/trends/microbiology/fulltext/S0966-842X(12)00082-0">https://www.cell.com/trends/microbiology/fulltext/S0966-842X(12)00082-0</a></li><li>Biodesign Challenge <a href="https://biodesignchallenge.org/">https://biodesignchallenge.org/</a></li><li>Backyard Brains  <a href="https://backyardbrains.com/">https://backyardbrains.com/</a></li></ul></li></ul>



<figure class="wp-block-image is-resized"><img decoding="async" src="http://astrobio.freaklab.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/09/69363915_2121742104797092_440698171811692544_n.png" alt="" class="wp-image-196" width="1024" srcset="https://astrobio.freaklab.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/09/69363915_2121742104797092_440698171811692544_n.png 1000w, https://astrobio.freaklab.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/09/69363915_2121742104797092_440698171811692544_n-300x230.png 300w, https://astrobio.freaklab.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/09/69363915_2121742104797092_440698171811692544_n-768x588.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Homeworks</strong></h2>



<p>Create a 2 minutes video pitch for Mars Colonization using Biomimicry, Synthetic Biology, Biodesign, and Bio-digital. In the video, please describe how do you plan to tackle the &#8220;Grand Challenges&#8221; using biotechnology using images, diagram, animation, and other digital media. Please post the video on youtube, and post the link down below.</p>



